          "value": {
            "data": {
              "entityKey": "5afdde79-9a43-4ad9-a1ea-e731e6878620",
              "markdown": "```json\n// package.jsonに以下を追加する\n{\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"axios\": \"1.14.0\"\n  },\n  \"overrides\": {\n    \"axios\": \"1.14.0\"\n  }\n}\n```"
            },
            "mutability": "Mutable",
            "type": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "4",
          "value": {
            "data": {
              "entityKey": "0f52abb6-875a-4350-84bd-eb58bf14e7a6",
              "markdown": "```\n# 感染を確認する（このフォルダがあれば感染している可能性が高いです）\nls node_modules/plain-crypto-js\n```"
            },
            "mutability": "Mutable",
            "type": "MARKDOWN"
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "11",
          "value": {
            "data": {
